    "long_instructions": "## Investigative Journalism\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze an image from a news article alongside a PDF of the article.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Upload one of the **images** from the Library. **Copy and paste** the following prompt:\r\n\r\n> Analyze this image. Then write a catchy newspaper headline for the image. \r\n\r\n2. Look at the **PDFs** from the Library and choose the article that best matches the **image** you picked in Step 1. Upload that **same image** again along with the **matching article PDF**.\r\n\r\n> Analyze this image and article together. Write a catchy newspaper headline that fits with the image and article.\r\n\r\n3. Read AI Chat's response.\r\n4. **Experiment**: \r\n   - **Modify your prompt** by describing the image as well as uploading the image and PDF.\r\n   - **Change your input document or image** to see how AI’s response changes.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**",
